    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="postcard">
                <pb facs="#Michele_seconda"/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date>10-12-1915</date>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>
                    	<presentation> 
                        	<recipient>Mrs. <persName ref="Celeste_Boscelli">Longhi Delfina Borgarello</persName>, <placeName ref="Torre_Del_Marghero">Torre del Marghero, Parma</placeName><br/></recipient>
                        	Dearest sister <persName ref="Celeste_Boscelli">Delfina</persName>
                    	</presentation>
                    </salute>
                </opener>
                <p> 
                    I came to know that <persName ref="Mother">mom</persName> is at your house so I write you  
                    <persName ref="Delfina_Villa">Delfina</persName>,  am fine and so I hope for you and our dear 
                    <persName ref="Mother">mom</persName> and your dear <persName ref="Kids">children</persName> 
                    <persName ref="Delfina_Villa">Delfina</persName> tell <persName ref="Mother">mom</persName> söyle () 
                    and that she eats without malincony <br/> since at the present I wont run into danger. <br/>
                    <persName ref="Creator">Villa Michele</persName>, Private, 112 Infantry, Company 11
                </p>
                <closer>
                    For now receive my affectionate regards to <persName ref="Delfina_Villa">you</persName> and our dear <persName ref="Mother">mom</persName> and a thousand kisses to your dear <persName ref="Kids">children</persName>. <br/>
                    <persName ref="Creator">Villa Michele</persName>
                    <signed></signed>
            	</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
